MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-2496. LiTel Telecommunications Corp. v. Tracy.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 91-A-1524. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective November 14, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
